channel.title: Cache downloading error
channel.description:
Hey,
Basically I setup up my client to download cache updates from my website. It works perfect for my 317 cache then I changed client to load 377 cache (commenting the two lines). When I try to load the 377 cache from my website it loads properly but then when finished and extracting I get this error
[CODE] RS2 user client - release #317 Extracting: main_file_cache.dat java.io.EOFException: Unexpected end of ZLIB input stream at java.util.zip.InflaterInputStream.fill(Unknown Source) at java.util.zip.InflaterInputStream.read(Unknown Source) at java.util.zip.ZipInputStream.read(Unknown Source) at FileDownload.unZip(FileDownload.java:36) at client.method6(client.java:6884) at Applet_Sub1.run(Applet_Sub1.java:51) at client.run(client.java:4527) at java.lang.Thread.run(Unknown Source)
[/CODE][br][br][size=1]Posted on: May 21, 2009, 05:09:44 pm[/size][hr]come on someone has to know
